---
title: Cheesy Beef Quesadillas & Salsa for Dinner with Tex-Mex Beef & Herby Rice for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new twist on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! Start with easy oven-baked quesadillas for dinner, then pop the extra beef mixture and some quick herby rice in a container to enjoy for lunch the next day. Extra delicious!

